	<Title>
		Emphysema: Does cold weather make it worse?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		In some people with emphysema, breathing cold air can cause narrowing of the airways.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Does cold weather worsen emphysema symptoms? I&apos;m thinking about moving from Florida to Indiana.
	</Question>
